title: Football Focus - 31st January 2015 - 720p x264
description:
SPORT: Football Focus
On: BBC 1 HD
Date: Saturday 31st January 2015
Time: 12:10 to 12:50

Dan Walker and guests take an in-depth look at the weekend's football fixtures,
  the highlight being the eagerly awaited clash between early season pacesetters
  Chelsea and Manchester City at Stamford Bridge. Other highlights on a busy day
  of Premier League action include Manchester United's meeting with Leicester City
  at Old Trafford, with Louis van Gaal's side looking to avenge September's shock
  5-3 defeat, while Liverpool take on Sam Allardyce's West Ham side at Anfield.
